cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.IR. 

The paper deals with object detection in remote sensing images, which is a computer vision problem, hence cs.CV is the most likely sub-category. The use of deep learning techniques and loss functions also suggests cs.AI and cs.LG as possible sub-categories. The paper also involves region proposal and non-maximum suppression, which are related to robotics and optimization, respectively, hence cs.RO is another possible sub-category. Finally, the paper deals with aerial and satellite imagery, which is related to information retrieval, hence cs.IR is a less likely but still possible sub-category.
